{"tid":2045132,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"真巧合！德國總理默克爾同希特拉女兒生得幾似樣","createTime":"2020-05-31T14:52:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T18:20:59.000Z","uid":48040,"like":56,"dislike":111,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"3e77b406f55f05953735c87a0e562b696213af7b","tid":2045132,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T14:52:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gmw2XpW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgmw2XpW.jpg&h=d0264e01&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁就難怪，默克爾最近向蝗國暗送秋波啦～<br />\nSource: HK01<br />\n《默克爾：要有決心承認中國在國際機構佔有一席之地》<br />\n默克爾5月27日強調，德中關係必須成為外交重點，不僅在貿易範圍內<span style=\"color: orange;\">，要有決心承認中國在國際機構當中佔有的一席之地，在氣候變化、環境保護以及衛生安全領域也可以而且必須與中國更進一步的合作。</span>「德國擔任歐洲聯盟理事會主席國時，德中外交關係會是一個優先項目。」<br />\n<br />\n=====<br />\n黃channel撐得很辛苦。你可以幫手subscribe及share嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0iBFBs1MH3I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0iBFBs1MH3I&d=jFWDEiyvEellqADaqpERGhphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=16b322a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0iBFBs1MH3I</a>"},{"pid":"3cd4957cce7527ad4b66b67fd69f6d64bc3794f8","tid":2045132,"uid":71037,"like":42,"dislike":6,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T14:53:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">納 粹 遺 物 － 東 德 共 產 肥 婆</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"aa09882d122115efee7267a8d293bf30b3bb681b","tid":2045132,"uid":48040,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"3cd4957cce7527ad4b66b67fd69f6d64bc3794f8","tid":2045132,"uid":71037,"like":42,"dislike":6,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T14:53:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">納 粹 遺 物 － 東 德 共 產 肥 婆</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T14:55:36.000Z","msg":"駁唔到<br />\n不過，睇返新聞，原來佢09年嗰時同達賴喇嘛見面，激怒北京。後尾可能見利忘義。"},{"pid":"7dcfd59472272618298c2f4bca52555e4be3f5f2","tid":2045132,"uid":227769,"like":